Many thanks to Jim Carrey who has recently announced the sale of his New York apartment. From the apartment, valued at $13.6 million, Jim Carrey has pledged over 50% of the sale to various charities including St Judes, the Children’s Miracle Network, Feeding America, Habitat for Humanity and several others.
